{
  "video_id": "0anZBvnj6LM",
  "title": "Future in English - How to Talk about the Future",
  "es": 0,
  "json": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "start_time": 1410.0,
      "end_time": 3740.0,
      "text": "Hi, I’m Martin."
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 3740.0,
      "end_time": 6840.0,
      "text": "Welcome to Oxford Online English!"
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 6840.0,
      "end_time": 12600.0,
      "text": "In this lesson, you can learn how to talk\r\nabout the future in English."
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 12600.0,
      "end_time": 15450.0,
      "text": "What are you doing this evening?"
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 15450.0,
      "end_time": 18189.0,
      "text": "What are your plans for next year?"
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 18189.0,
      "end_time": 20850.0,
      "text": "Who will win the next World Cup?"
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 20850.0,
      "end_time": 25680.0,
      "text": "In this class, you’ll learn to answer these\r\nand other questions about the future in clear,"
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 25680.0,
      "end_time": 27609.0,
      "text": "natural, correct English."
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 27609.0,
      "end_time": 34230.0,
      "text": "You’ll see many simple phrases which you\r\ncan learn to help you talk about the future"
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 34230.0,
      "end_time": 37860.0,
      "text": "in English in any situation!"
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 37860.0,
      "end_time": 42840.0,
      "text": "Let’s start with a simple question: what\r\nare you doing this weekend?"
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 46440.0,
      "end_time": 47680.0,
      "text": "What are you doing this weekend?"
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 47680.0,
      "end_time": 52050.0,
      "text": "I’m meeting some friends for lunch on Saturday,\r\nand then we’re going to the theatre."
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 52050.0,
      "end_time": 53890.0,
      "text": "Sounds good!"
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 53890.0,
      "end_time": 55450.0,
      "text": "What about Sunday?"
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 55450.0,
      "end_time": 56450.0,
      "text": "Not sure."
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 56450.0,
      "end_time": 57680.0,
      "text": "I don’t have plans yet."
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 57680.0,
      "end_time": 60160.0,
      "text": "What about you—doing anything fun?"
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 60160.0,
      "end_time": 62620.0,
      "text": "I’m going away for the weekend."
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 62620.0,
      "end_time": 63620.0,
      "text": "Really?"
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 63620.0,
      "end_time": 64620.0,
      "text": "Nice!"
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 64620.00000000001,
      "end_time": 65620.0,
      "text": "Where are you going?"
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 65620.0,
      "end_time": 66620.0,
      "text": "Berlin!"
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 66620.0,
      "end_time": 69020.0,
      "text": "I found some cheap flights."
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 69020.0,
      "end_time": 72910.0,
      "text": "Let’s look at some useful language you saw\r\nin this dialogue:"
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 72910.0,
      "end_time": 75230.0,
      "text": "What are you doing this weekend?"
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 75230.0,
      "end_time": 77220.0,
      "text": "This is a very common question."
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 77220.0,
      "end_time": 80640.0,
      "text": "You can change it and use it in different\r\nsituations, like this:"
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 80640.0,
      "end_time": 83750.0,
      "text": "What are you doing tomorrow?"
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 83750.0,
      "end_time": 84750.0,
      "text": "What are you doing tonight?"
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 84750.0,
      "end_time": 87940.0,
      "text": "What are you doing next Wednesday evening?"
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 87940.0,
      "end_time": 92640.0,
      "text": "How could you answer these three questions?"
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 92640.0,
      "end_time": 95960.0,
      "text": "Here are some possible answers:"
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 95960.0,
      "end_time": 100880.0,
      "text": "I’m working in the morning, then I’m playing\r\nfootball in the park with some friends."
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 100880.0,
      "end_time": 104400.0,
      "text": "I’m going for a beer with some people from\r\nwork."
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 104400.0,
      "end_time": 105400.0,
      "text": "Next Wednesday?"
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 105400.0,
      "end_time": 106400.0,
      "text": "No idea!"
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 106400.0,
      "end_time": 109770.0,
      "text": "I haven’t made any plans yet."
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 109770.0,
      "end_time": 117860.0,
      "text": "Can you see what verb form you need in these\r\nquestions and answers?"
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 117860.0,
      "end_time": 120580.0,
      "text": "You often need the present continuous tense."
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 120580.0,
      "end_time": 124840.0,
      "text": "You can use the present continuous to talk\r\nabout the future, even though it’s a present"
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 124840.0,
      "end_time": 125840.0,
      "text": "tense."
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 125840.0,
      "end_time": 129640.0,
      "text": "You can use the present continuous to talk\r\nabout plans if you know where or when something"
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 129639.99999999999,
      "end_time": 131100.0,
      "text": "will happen."
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 131100.0,
      "end_time": 134390.0,
      "text": "Usually, you use it to talk about the near\r\nfuture."
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 134390.0,
      "end_time": 139480.0,
      "text": "However, you can also use it for plans which\r\nare further in the future, like holiday plans."
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 139480.0,
      "end_time": 143910.0,
      "text": "Let’s see some examples of this:\r\nAre you going anywhere next summer?"
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 143910.0,
      "end_time": 145720.0,
      "text": "We’re going to Cornwall."
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 145720.0,
      "end_time": 148420.0,
      "text": "It’s the same place we go every year."
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 148430.0,
      "end_time": 150660.0,
      "text": "I’ve heard it’s beautiful there!"
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start_time": 150660.0,
      "end_time": 152850.0,
      "text": "How long are you staying there?"
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 152850.0,
      "end_time": 154000.0,
      "text": "Just a week."
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 154000.0,
      "end_time": 155390.0,
      "text": "Are you going in July?"
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "start_time": 155390.0,
      "end_time": 158900.0,
      "text": "I’m thinking about going, just for two or\r\nthree days."
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "start_time": 158900.0,
      "end_time": 160410.0,
      "text": "No, we’re going in August."
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "start_time": 160410.0,
      "end_time": 162090.0,
      "text": "Who are you going with?"
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "start_time": 162090.0,
      "end_time": 164980.0,
      "text": "I’m going with two old college friends."
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "start_time": 164980.0,
      "end_time": 168710.0,
      "text": "Well, if you come in August, we can show you\r\naround!"
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "start_time": 168710.0,
      "end_time": 172030.0,
      "text": "I’m working in August, unfortunately."
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "start_time": 172030.0,
      "end_time": 179430.0,
      "text": "Here, you heard useful questions to ask someone\r\nabout their vacation plans:"
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "start_time": 179430.0,
      "end_time": 181810.0,
      "text": "Are you going anywhere this summer?"
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "start_time": 181810.0,
      "end_time": 183830.0,
      "text": "How long are you staying there?"
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "start_time": 183830.0,
      "end_time": 185760.0,
      "text": "Who are you going with?"
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "start_time": 185760.0,
      "end_time": 189390.0,
      "text": "Can you answer these three questions?"
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "start_time": 189390.0,
      "end_time": 195500.0,
      "text": "Pause the video and make your own answers."
    },
    {
      "index": 66,
      "start_time": 195500.0,
      "end_time": 199790.0,
      "text": "Now, put your answers together in one sentence,\r\nlike this:"
    },
    {
      "index": 67,
      "start_time": 199790.0,
      "end_time": 203560.0,
      "text": "I’m going to Egypt for 10 days with a group\r\nof friends."
    },
    {
      "index": 68,
      "start_time": 203560.0,
      "end_time": 207510.0,
      "text": "Next, add some more details about what you’re\r\nplanning to do!"
    },
    {
      "index": 69,
      "start_time": 207510.0,
      "end_time": 208560.0,
      "text": "For example:"
    },
    {
      "index": 70,
      "start_time": 208560.0,
      "end_time": 212040.0,
      "text": "I’m going to Egypt for 10 days with a group\r\nof friends."
    },
    {
      "index": 71,
      "start_time": 212040.0,
      "end_time": 216130.0,
      "text": "We’re planning to do some sightseeing around\r\nCairo, then we’re going to do a boat trip"
    },
    {
      "index": 72,
      "start_time": 216130.0,
      "end_time": 217870.0,
      "text": "on the Nile."
    },
    {
      "index": 73,
      "start_time": 217870.0,
      "end_time": 222030.0,
      "text": "Can you see something different in this sentence?"
    },
    {
      "index": 74,
      "start_time": 222030.0,
      "end_time": 223500.0,
      "text": "We said:"
    },
    {
      "index": 75,
      "start_time": 223500.0,
      "end_time": 228709.0,
      "text": "We’re planning to do some sightseeing around\r\nCairo."
    },
    {
      "index": 76,
      "start_time": 228709.0,
      "end_time": 233330.0,
      "text": "We’re going to do a boat trip on the Nile."
    },
    {
      "index": 77,
      "start_time": 233330.0,
      "end_time": 239920.0,
      "text": "Here, you’re using two verbs: planning to\r\ndo and going to do."
    },
    {
      "index": 78,
      "start_time": 239920.0,
      "end_time": 242190.0,
      "text": "Do you know why?"
    },
    {
      "index": 79,
      "start_time": 242190.0,
      "end_time": 244880.0,
      "text": "Let’s see the answer:"
    },
    {
      "index": 80,
      "start_time": 247620.0,
      "end_time": 250780.0,
      "text": "You use the present\r\ncontinuous to talk about plans if you know"
    },
    {
      "index": 81,
      "start_time": 250780.0,
      "end_time": 253790.0,
      "text": "where or when something will happen."
    },
    {
      "index": 82,
      "start_time": 253790.0,
      "end_time": 258660.0,
      "text": "That means you often need the present continuous\r\nto talk about plans in the near future."
    },
    {
      "index": 83,
      "start_time": 258660.00000000003,
      "end_time": 262920.0,
      "text": "What about plans in the future if you don’t\r\nknow exactly where or when things will happen?"
    },
    {
      "index": 84,
      "start_time": 262920.0,
      "end_time": 264780.0,
      "text": "Is it true?"
    },
    {
      "index": 85,
      "start_time": 264780.0,
      "end_time": 266040.0,
      "text": "You quit?"
    },
    {
      "index": 86,
      "start_time": 266040.0,
      "end_time": 267040.0,
      "text": "Yes!"
    },
    {
      "index": 87,
      "start_time": 267040.0,
      "end_time": 272120.0,
      "text": "I’m done with this place, and it feels great!"
    },
    {
      "index": 88,
      "start_time": 272120.0,
      "end_time": 274270.0,
      "text": "What are you going to do now?"
    },
    {
      "index": 89,
      "start_time": 274270.0,
      "end_time": 280800.0,
      "text": "You know, first of all I’m planning to take\r\nsome time to rest and recover my energy."
    },
    {
      "index": 90,
      "start_time": 280800.0,
      "end_time": 284990.0,
      "text": "I’ve been so stressed the last few months."
    },
    {
      "index": 91,
      "start_time": 284990.0,
      "end_time": 288210.0,
      "text": "Sure, but then how are you going to find a\r\nnew job?"
    },
    {
      "index": 92,
      "start_time": 288210.0,
      "end_time": 291639.0,
      "text": "Actually, I’d like to start my own business."
    },
    {
      "index": 93,
      "start_time": 291639.0,
      "end_time": 294889.0,
      "text": "I’m tired of working for other people."
    },
    {
      "index": 94,
      "start_time": 294889.0,
      "end_time": 295889.0,
      "text": "Really?"
    },
    {
      "index": 95,
      "start_time": 295889.0,
      "end_time": 298410.0,
      "text": "What kind of thing are you thinking of doing?"
    },
    {
      "index": 96,
      "start_time": 298410.0,
      "end_time": 303600.0,
      "text": "My dream is to have my own small marketing\r\nfirm."
    },
    {
      "index": 97,
      "start_time": 303600.0,
      "end_time": 309020.0,
      "text": "I’m hoping to start with freelancing, and\r\nthen build up from there."
    },
    {
      "index": 98,
      "start_time": 309020.0,
      "end_time": 311190.0,
      "text": "Wow—good luck!"
    },
    {
      "index": 99,
      "start_time": 311190.0,
      "end_time": 317810.0,
      "text": "Here, you saw useful phrases to talk about\r\nplans if you don’t know all the details"
    },
    {
      "index": 100,
      "start_time": 317810.0,
      "end_time": 318810.0,
      "text": "yet."
    },
    {
      "index": 101,
      "start_time": 318810.0,
      "end_time": 324700.0,
      "text": "Do you remember any of the questions and phrases?"
    },
    {
      "index": 102,
      "start_time": 324700.0,
      "end_time": 328000.0,
      "text": "Here’s some of the key language you saw:"
    },
    {
      "index": 103,
      "start_time": 328000.0,
      "end_time": 330230.0,
      "text": "What are you going to do now?"
    },
    {
      "index": 104,
      "start_time": 330230.0,
      "end_time": 333430.0,
      "text": "I’m planning to take some time to rest."
    },
    {
      "index": 105,
      "start_time": 333430.0,
      "end_time": 337160.0,
      "text": "I’d like to start my own business."
    },
    {
      "index": 106,
      "start_time": 337160.0,
      "end_time": 340020.0,
      "text": "My dream is to have my own marketing firm."
    },
    {
      "index": 107,
      "start_time": 340020.0,
      "end_time": 346940.0,
      "text": "You can change these sentences to fit different\r\nsituations, like this:"
    },
    {
      "index": 108,
      "start_time": 346940.0,
      "end_time": 350020.0,
      "text": "What are you going to do after you graduate?"
    },
    {
      "index": 109,
      "start_time": 350020.0,
      "end_time": 353860.0,
      "text": "I’m planning to buy an apartment next year."
    },
    {
      "index": 110,
      "start_time": 353860.0,
      "end_time": 357780.0,
      "text": "I’d like to learn to scuba dive one day."
    },
    {
      "index": 111,
      "start_time": 357780.0,
      "end_time": 363840.0,
      "text": "My dream is to live near the sea, where it’s\r\nsunny all year round."
    },
    {
      "index": 112,
      "start_time": 363840.0,
      "end_time": 370290.0,
      "text": "You can use these to talk about future plans,\r\ndreams and ideas."
    },
    {
      "index": 113,
      "start_time": 370290.0,
      "end_time": 371480.0,
      "text": "What about you?"
    },
    {
      "index": 114,
      "start_time": 371480.0,
      "end_time": 379400.0,
      "text": "What are your plans, dreams and ideas for\r\nthe future?"
    },
    {
      "index": 115,
      "start_time": 379400.0,
      "end_time": 383229.0,
      "text": "Use these templates and make four sentences\r\nabout your life and your plans."
    },
    {
      "index": 116,
      "start_time": 383229.0,
      "end_time": 387610.0,
      "text": "Say the sentences aloud, or write them down,\r\nor both!"
    },
    {
      "index": 117,
      "start_time": 387610.0,
      "end_time": 392690.0,
      "text": "Now, you know how to talk about all kinds\r\nof future plans in English."
    },
    {
      "index": 118,
      "start_time": 392690.0,
      "end_time": 399400.0,
      "text": "What other things do you need to talk about\r\nin the future?"
    },
    {
      "index": 119,
      "start_time": 399400.0,
      "end_time": 401229.0,
      "text": "What time does the concert start?"
    },
    {
      "index": 120,
      "start_time": 401229.0,
      "end_time": 403419.0,
      "text": "8.00, so we need to leave at 6.30."
    },
    {
      "index": 121,
      "start_time": 403419.0,
      "end_time": 405600.0,
      "text": "Is there a bus?"
    },
    {
      "index": 122,
      "start_time": 405600.0,
      "end_time": 411010.0,
      "text": "Yeah, I think it leaves at 6.45, and it gets\r\nthere around 7.30."
    },
    {
      "index": 123,
      "start_time": 411010.0,
      "end_time": 412180.0,
      "text": "What time does it finish?"
    },
    {
      "index": 124,
      "start_time": 412180.0,
      "end_time": 414550.0,
      "text": "It’s supposed to end at ten."
    },
    {
      "index": 125,
      "start_time": 414550.0,
      "end_time": 419009.0,
      "text": "The last bus back leaves at 10.15, so we’ll\r\nhave to hurry."
    },
    {
      "index": 126,
      "start_time": 419009.0,
      "end_time": 423790.0,
      "text": "Here, you saw us talking about schedules."
    },
    {
      "index": 127,
      "start_time": 423790.0,
      "end_time": 428150.0,
      "text": "Do you remember what language you heard?"
    },
    {
      "index": 128,
      "start_time": 428150.0,
      "end_time": 432669.0,
      "text": "You can use the present simple to talk about\r\nfuture schedules or timetables."
    },
    {
      "index": 129,
      "start_time": 432669.0,
      "end_time": 434669.0,
      "text": "For example:"
    },
    {
      "index": 130,
      "start_time": 434669.0,
      "end_time": 436729.0,
      "text": "What time does the concert start?"
    },
    {
      "index": 131,
      "start_time": 436729.0,
      "end_time": 440210.0,
      "text": "The bus gets there around 7.30."
    },
    {
      "index": 132,
      "start_time": 440210.0,
      "end_time": 443460.0,
      "text": "The last bus leaves at 10.15."
    },
    {
      "index": 133,
      "start_time": 443460.0,
      "end_time": 451070.0,
      "text": "You can use this to talk about public transport,\r\nclass timetables, work schedules, events,"
    },
    {
      "index": 134,
      "start_time": 451070.0,
      "end_time": 454940.0,
      "text": "or anything else which runs on a timetable."
    },
    {
      "index": 135,
      "start_time": 454940.0,
      "end_time": 457320.0,
      "text": "For example:"
    },
    {
      "index": 136,
      "start_time": 457320.0,
      "end_time": 460669.0,
      "text": "Our class starts at eleven thirty."
    },
    {
      "index": 137,
      "start_time": 460669.0,
      "end_time": 462509.0,
      "text": "What time is your flight?"
    },
    {
      "index": 138,
      "start_time": 462509.0,
      "end_time": 464259.0,
      "text": "The wedding is at three."
    },
    {
      "index": 139,
      "start_time": 464259.0,
      "end_time": 466580.0,
      "text": "Now, it’s your turn!"
    },
    {
      "index": 140,
      "start_time": 466580.0,
      "end_time": 469990.0,
      "text": "Think of three things in your life which run\r\non a timetable."
    },
    {
      "index": 141,
      "start_time": 469990.0,
      "end_time": 473100.0,
      "text": "Make three sentences using the present simple."
    },
    {
      "index": 142,
      "start_time": 473100.0,
      "end_time": 474680.0,
      "text": "Want an extra challenge?"
    },
    {
      "index": 143,
      "start_time": 474680.0,
      "end_time": 477240.0,
      "text": "Make questions and answers, like this:"
    },
    {
      "index": 144,
      "start_time": 477240.0,
      "end_time": 479630.0,
      "text": "What time does the train leave?"
    },
    {
      "index": 145,
      "start_time": 479630.0,
      "end_time": 481050.0,
      "text": "It leaves at five thirty."
    },
    {
      "index": 146,
      "start_time": 481050.0,
      "end_time": 484860.0,
      "text": "Pause the video and make your three sentences\r\nnow."
    },
    {
      "index": 147,
      "start_time": 484860.0,
      "end_time": 489780.0,
      "text": "Again, write them down if you want some extra\r\npractice."
    },
    {
      "index": 148,
      "start_time": 489780.0,
      "end_time": 491420.0,
      "text": "Ooh!"
    },
    {
      "index": 149,
      "start_time": 491430.0,
      "end_time": 494910.0,
      "text": "We forgot something… a very important question."
    },
    {
      "index": 150,
      "start_time": 494910.0,
      "end_time": 495910.0,
      "text": "Oh?"
    },
    {
      "index": 151,
      "start_time": 495910.0,
      "end_time": 497670.0,
      "text": "What’s that?"
    },
    {
      "index": 152,
      "start_time": 497670.0,
      "end_time": 499630.0,
      "text": "You don’t remember?"
    },
    {
      "index": 153,
      "start_time": 499630.0,
      "end_time": 503380.0,
      "text": "At the beginning: who’s going to win the\r\nnext World Cup?"
    },
    {
      "index": 154,
      "start_time": 507360.0,
      "end_time": 509320.0,
      "text": "What do you think?"
    },
    {
      "index": 155,
      "start_time": 509320.0,
      "end_time": 512260.0,
      "text": "Maybe you said something like:"
    },
    {
      "index": 156,
      "start_time": 512260.0,
      "end_time": 514130.0,
      "text": "Italy will win."
    },
    {
      "index": 157,
      "start_time": 514130.0,
      "end_time": 519110.0,
      "text": "I hope Russia will win, but I don’t think\r\nthey actually will."
    },
    {
      "index": 158,
      "start_time": 519110.0,
      "end_time": 522000.0,
      "text": "England definitely won’t win it."
    },
    {
      "index": 159,
      "start_time": 522000.0,
      "end_time": 529279.0,
      "text": "To make predictions about the future, you\r\ncan use will or won’t."
    },
    {
      "index": 160,
      "start_time": 529279.0,
      "end_time": 531559.0,
      "text": "You can also use going to."
    },
    {
      "index": 161,
      "start_time": 531559.0,
      "end_time": 535910.0,
      "text": "You generally use going to for predictions\r\nthat are not so far in the future:"
    },
    {
      "index": 162,
      "start_time": 535910.0,
      "end_time": 540279.0,
      "text": "It’s going to rain—look at those clouds."
    },
    {
      "index": 163,
      "start_time": 540279.0,
      "end_time": 542470.0,
      "text": "What do you think is going to happen next?"
    },
    {
      "index": 164,
      "start_time": 542470.0,
      "end_time": 546889.0,
      "text": "He’s going to be unhappy when he finds out\r\nabout this."
    },
    {
      "index": 165,
      "start_time": 546889.0,
      "end_time": 551540.0,
      "text": "That said, don’t worry about the difference\r\nbetween will and going to here."
    },
    {
      "index": 166,
      "start_time": 551540.0,
      "end_time": 554860.0,
      "text": "You can use both freely—no one will notice."
    },
    {
      "index": 167,
      "start_time": 554860.0,
      "end_time": 557569.0,
      "text": "You can also use many other phrases to make\r\npredictions."
    },
    {
      "index": 168,
      "start_time": 557569.0,
      "end_time": 561260.0,
      "text": "Let’s look:\r\nSo, do you think they’ll do it?"
    },
    {
      "index": 169,
      "start_time": 561260.0,
      "end_time": 564050.0,
      "text": "Michelle will definitely do it."
    },
    {
      "index": 170,
      "start_time": 564050.0,
      "end_time": 566740.0,
      "text": "There’s no chance Andy is going to finish."
    },
    {
      "index": 171,
      "start_time": 566740.0,
      "end_time": 573009.0,
      "text": "He doesn’t look like he can run to the bus\r\nstop, so I can’t believe he’ll run 26"
    },
    {
      "index": 172,
      "start_time": 573009.0,
      "end_time": 574840.0,
      "text": "miles."
    },
    {
      "index": 173,
      "start_time": 574840.0,
      "end_time": 575920.0,
      "text": "I don’t know."
    },
    {
      "index": 174,
      "start_time": 575920.0,
      "end_time": 577290.0,
      "text": "He’s been training hard."
    },
    {
      "index": 175,
      "start_time": 577290.0,
      "end_time": 581540.0,
      "text": "He’s unlikely to get a fast time, but I’m\r\npretty sure he’ll do it."
    },
    {
      "index": 176,
      "start_time": 581540.0,
      "end_time": 587439.0,
      "text": "Well, anyway, we can agree that Michelle is\r\nsure to be much faster!"
    },
    {
      "index": 177,
      "start_time": 587439.0,
      "end_time": 589300.0,
      "text": "Yeah, of course."
    },
    {
      "index": 178,
      "start_time": 589300.0,
      "end_time": 591800.0,
      "text": "Do you think she’ll do it in under three\r\nhours?"
    },
    {
      "index": 179,
      "start_time": 591800.0,
      "end_time": 595990.0,
      "text": "It’s not likely that she’ll do it that\r\nfast."
    },
    {
      "index": 180,
      "start_time": 595990.0,
      "end_time": 599329.0,
      "text": "Under three hours for a marathon is quick."
    },
    {
      "index": 181,
      "start_time": 599329.0,
      "end_time": 602509.0,
      "text": "But, she’s bound to get under four hours."
    },
    {
      "index": 182,
      "start_time": 602509.0,
      "end_time": 604730.0,
      "text": "That’s still a good time."
    },
    {
      "index": 183,
      "start_time": 604730.0,
      "end_time": 611689.0,
      "text": "There, we were talking about two people running\r\na marathon, and making predictions about how"
    },
    {
      "index": 184,
      "start_time": 611689.0,
      "end_time": 613310.0,
      "text": "they would do."
    },
    {
      "index": 185,
      "start_time": 613310.0,
      "end_time": 621790.0,
      "text": "Apart from will and going to, did you notice\r\nany other language we used to make predictions"
    },
    {
      "index": 186,
      "start_time": 621790.0,
      "end_time": 625480.0,
      "text": "about the future?"
    },
    {
      "index": 187,
      "start_time": 625480.0,
      "end_time": 630940.0,
      "text": "Firstly, you can modify will or going to by\r\nadding an adverb, like this:"
    },
    {
      "index": 188,
      "start_time": 630940.0,
      "end_time": 633029.0,
      "text": "She’ll definitely do it."
    },
    {
      "index": 189,
      "start_time": 633029.0,
      "end_time": 635910.0,
      "text": "There’s no chance he’s going to finish."
    },
    {
      "index": 190,
      "start_time": 635910.0,
      "end_time": 638489.0,
      "text": "I’m pretty sure he’ll do it."
    },
    {
      "index": 191,
      "start_time": 638489.0,
      "end_time": 642600.0,
      "text": "In this way, you can show that you’re more\r\nor less sure about your prediction."
    },
    {
      "index": 192,
      "start_time": 642600.0,
      "end_time": 648550.0,
      "text": "You also heard some other phrases you can\r\nuse to make predictions in the future:"
    },
    {
      "index": 193,
      "start_time": 648550.0,
      "end_time": 651040.0,
      "text": "He’s unlikely to get a fast time."
    },
    {
      "index": 194,
      "start_time": 651040.0,
      "end_time": 654100.0,
      "text": "She’s sure to be much faster."
    },
    {
      "index": 195,
      "start_time": 654100.0,
      "end_time": 657199.0,
      "text": "It’s not likely that she’ll do it that\r\nfast."
    },
    {
      "index": 196,
      "start_time": 657199.0,
      "end_time": 661560.0,
      "text": "She’s bound to get under four hours."
    },
    {
      "index": 197,
      "start_time": 661560.0,
      "end_time": 664129.0,
      "text": "Likely has a similar meaning to probable."
    },
    {
      "index": 198,
      "start_time": 664129.0,
      "end_time": 669249.0,
      "text": "Be careful, because likely is an adjective,\r\nnot an adverb."
    },
    {
      "index": 199,
      "start_time": 669249.0,
      "end_time": 676600.0,
      "text": "So, if you say He’s unlikely to get a fast\r\ntime, you mean that he’ll probably be quite"
    },
    {
      "index": 200,
      "start_time": 676600.0,
      "end_time": 678600.0,
      "text": "slow."
    },
    {
      "index": 201,
      "start_time": 678600.0,
      "end_time": 684800.0,
      "text": "Sure to and bound to both mean that you’re\r\nabsolutely certain about something."
    },
    {
      "index": 202,
      "start_time": 684800.0,
      "end_time": 688980.0,
      "text": "You can use them to emphasise how sure you\r\nare."
    },
    {
      "index": 203,
      "start_time": 688980.0,
      "end_time": 691760.0,
      "text": "These phrases are a little less common."
    },
    {
      "index": 204,
      "start_time": 691760.0,
      "end_time": 697180.0,
      "text": "However, they are good to know, so you can\r\nadd variety to your spoken English."
    },
    {
      "index": 205,
      "start_time": 697199.0,
      "end_time": 700610.0,
      "text": "Let’s see how you could use these phrases\r\nin some other ways:"
    },
    {
      "index": 206,
      "start_time": 700610.0,
      "end_time": 704629.0,
      "text": "They’re unlikely to hire you if you have\r\nso little experience."
    },
    {
      "index": 207,
      "start_time": 704629.0,
      "end_time": 708769.0,
      "text": "It’s exactly your kind of film—you’re\r\nsure to like it."
    },
    {
      "index": 208,
      "start_time": 708769.0,
      "end_time": 711899.0,
      "text": "It’s not likely that I’ll wake up before\r\nnine."
    },
    {
      "index": 209,
      "start_time": 711899.0,
      "end_time": 717529.0,
      "text": "He’s a really good cook; whatever he makes,\r\nit’s bound to be delicious."
    },
    {
      "index": 210,
      "start_time": 717529.0,
      "end_time": 722619.0,
      "text": "Note also that likely can be used with both\r\na positive and a negative meaning."
    },
    {
      "index": 211,
      "start_time": 722619.0,
      "end_time": 727860.0,
      "text": "You can say It’s unlikely that… or He’s\r\nnot likely to…"
    },
    {
      "index": 212,
      "start_time": 727860.0,
      "end_time": 731420.0,
      "text": "However, sure to and bound to are always positive."
    },
    {
      "index": 213,
      "start_time": 731420.0,
      "end_time": 733440.0,
      "text": "Now, it’s your turn!"
    },
    {
      "index": 214,
      "start_time": 733440.0,
      "end_time": 737989.0,
      "text": "Pause the video and make four predictions\r\nabout the future."
    },
    {
      "index": 215,
      "start_time": 737989.0,
      "end_time": 743600.0,
      "text": "You could make predictions about the weather,\r\nsport, your life, or anything you like!"
    },
    {
      "index": 216,
      "start_time": 743600.0,
      "end_time": 750520.0,
      "text": "Make four sentences, say them aloud, and write\r\nthem down if you want extra practice."
    },
    {
      "index": 217,
      "start_time": 750520.0,
      "end_time": 751840.0,
      "text": "Done?"
    },
    {
      "index": 218,
      "start_time": 751840.0,
      "end_time": 755600.0,
      "text": "Next, let’s look at one more topic you need\r\nto talk about the future."
    },
    {
      "index": 219,
      "start_time": 758560.0,
      "end_time": 764299.0,
      "text": "Up to now, you’ve learned how to talk about\r\nthings in the future that you are certain"
    },
    {
      "index": 220,
      "start_time": 764299.0,
      "end_time": 765709.0,
      "text": "about."
    },
    {
      "index": 221,
      "start_time": 765709.0,
      "end_time": 769780.0,
      "text": "However, the future is often uncertain."
    },
    {
      "index": 222,
      "start_time": 769780.0,
      "end_time": 774060.0,
      "text": "How can you express this when you speak English?"
    },
    {
      "index": 223,
      "start_time": 774060.0,
      "end_time": 778100.0,
      "text": "Let’s look:\r\nSo, do you have any idea when you’ll have"
    },
    {
      "index": 224,
      "start_time": 778100.0,
      "end_time": 779920.0,
      "text": "finished everything?"
    },
    {
      "index": 225,
      "start_time": 779920.0,
      "end_time": 782320.0,
      "text": "It really depends."
    },
    {
      "index": 226,
      "start_time": 782320.0,
      "end_time": 786249.0,
      "text": "It may be ready next week if everything goes\r\nwell."
    },
    {
      "index": 227,
      "start_time": 786249.0,
      "end_time": 788230.0,
      "text": "We really need it done sooner."
    },
    {
      "index": 228,
      "start_time": 788230.0,
      "end_time": 794040.0,
      "text": "The thing is, it’s possible that we’ll\r\nhave to replace some of the artwork."
    },
    {
      "index": 229,
      "start_time": 794040.0,
      "end_time": 796639.0,
      "text": "That could take a few days."
    },
    {
      "index": 230,
      "start_time": 796639.0,
      "end_time": 801670.0,
      "text": "Ok, I have to ask: why are you making such\r\nbig changes so late?"
    },
    {
      "index": 231,
      "start_time": 801670.0,
      "end_time": 805809.0,
      "text": "For a project like this, those details should\r\nbe finalised by now."
    },
    {
      "index": 232,
      "start_time": 805809.0,
      "end_time": 811170.0,
      "text": "We had some issues, but anyway, let’s focus\r\non what we can do now."
    },
    {
      "index": 233,
      "start_time": 811170.0,
      "end_time": 813980.0,
      "text": "Perhaps we won’t need to change anything."
    },
    {
      "index": 234,
      "start_time": 813980.0,
      "end_time": 819639.0,
      "text": "In that case, it’ll definitely be finished\r\nby the end of next week."
    },
    {
      "index": 235,
      "start_time": 819639.0,
      "end_time": 821230.0,
      "text": "Even that’s too late."
    },
    {
      "index": 236,
      "start_time": 821230.0,
      "end_time": 824529.0,
      "text": "Look, you need to sort this out."
    },
    {
      "index": 237,
      "start_time": 824529.0,
      "end_time": 827290.0,
      "text": "Maybe I’ll work overtime this weekend."
    },
    {
      "index": 238,
      "start_time": 827290.0,
      "end_time": 829179.0,
      "text": "That might help."
    },
    {
      "index": 239,
      "start_time": 829180.0,
      "end_time": 831200.0,
      "text": "Just do what you have to."
    },
    {
      "index": 240,
      "start_time": 831200.0,
      "end_time": 837329.0,
      "text": "In this dialogue, I was an employee, and I\r\nwasn’t very sure about a lot of things."
    },
    {
      "index": 241,
      "start_time": 837329.0,
      "end_time": 843480.0,
      "text": "I used different words and phrases to show\r\nthat I wasn’t sure."
    },
    {
      "index": 242,
      "start_time": 843480.0,
      "end_time": 847929.0,
      "text": "Do you remember any of them?"
    },
    {
      "index": 243,
      "start_time": 847929.0,
      "end_time": 852110.0,
      "text": "You can use a modal verb like may, might or\r\ncould."
    },
    {
      "index": 244,
      "start_time": 852110.0,
      "end_time": 853600.0,
      "text": "For example:"
    },
    {
      "index": 245,
      "start_time": 853600.0,
      "end_time": 855809.0,
      "text": "It may be ready next week."
    },
    {
      "index": 246,
      "start_time": 855809.0,
      "end_time": 857910.0,
      "text": "That could take a few days."
    },
    {
      "index": 247,
      "start_time": 857910.0,
      "end_time": 860009.0,
      "text": "That might help."
    },
    {
      "index": 248,
      "start_time": 860009.0,
      "end_time": 864519.0,
      "text": "You can also use will with an adverb like\r\nperhaps or maybe."
    },
    {
      "index": 249,
      "start_time": 864519.0,
      "end_time": 868220.0,
      "text": "This has the same meaning as using verbs like\r\nmight or could."
    },
    {
      "index": 250,
      "start_time": 868220.0,
      "end_time": 870149.0,
      "text": "For example:"
    },
    {
      "index": 251,
      "start_time": 870149.0,
      "end_time": 872239.0,
      "text": "Perhaps we won’t need to change anything."
    },
    {
      "index": 252,
      "start_time": 872239.0,
      "end_time": 875889.0,
      "text": "Maybe I’ll work overtime this weekend."
    },
    {
      "index": 253,
      "start_time": 875889.0,
      "end_time": 880959.0,
      "text": "Finally, you can use the phrase it’s possible\r\nthat…, like this:"
    },
    {
      "index": 254,
      "start_time": 880959.0,
      "end_time": 884600.0,
      "text": "It’s possible that we’ll have to replace\r\nsome of the artwork."
    },
    {
      "index": 255,
      "start_time": 884600.0,
      "end_time": 890899.0,
      "text": "As with all of these sentences, you can change\r\nthem to express your own ideas."
    },
    {
      "index": 256,
      "start_time": 890899.0,
      "end_time": 891899.0,
      "text": "For example:"
    },
    {
      "index": 257,
      "start_time": 891899.0,
      "end_time": 894109.0,
      "text": "I may be away next week."
    },
    {
      "index": 258,
      "start_time": 894109.0,
      "end_time": 896800.0,
      "text": "Taking a warm coat might be a good idea."
    },
    {
      "index": 259,
      "start_time": 896800.0,
      "end_time": 900100.0,
      "text": "Perhaps I’ll go to the park for a walk this\r\nafternoon."
    },
    {
      "index": 260,
      "start_time": 900100.0,
      "end_time": 904569.0,
      "text": "It’s possible that she didn’t see your\r\nmessage."
    },
    {
      "index": 261,
      "start_time": 904569.0,
      "end_time": 912420.0,
